<title>BEYOND THE SWELLING FLOOD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thisana sawp vam puon silh in,
 Tuilien galah kituok hitiu;
 Ziechun natna umta puon tin,
 Kikhen himhim lau ta puoi tiu,

[V2]
 Tuilien kinawk galah.
 Tuilien kinawk galah (3)
 Zie chun kituok hitiu;
 Kikhen kit talo din (3)
 Tuilien kinawk galah.

[V3]
 2. Tun gim thuok mahleng ka lau puoi,
 Ginnan ka mui ka van In chuh;
 Angelte Aw gi chu ka za'i,
 &quot;Pathien in mitthi thiek hul ding&quot;
 Tuilien kinawk galah.

[V4]
 3. Guol deih kituok khawmna mun ah,
 Lamtuoh Aw kipah um zaitiu;
 I thagau uh kipak tana,
 Sana kawtkhak a I lut tieng,
 Tuilien kinawk galah.

[V5]
 4. Hukdampa, ka ma pui zelin,
 Kipahna bukim ka neih na'n;
 Hehpih na'n mitthi thiek hul ding,
 Hai loin chawian zing hitiu,
 Tuilien kinawk galah.</lyrics>
</song>